description:
Jase digs into the mysterious origins of Melchizedek. Not having a record of him isn't a big deal for us, but it was culturally a huge deal at the time of his appearance. Al talks about the plan of God, perfectly existing outside time and space. Jase shares one of his and Zach's favorite lines said by God in the Bible. Jase highlights that Jesus is the best thing that ever happened to humanity. And Phil gives a genealogy of his pets and how Bobo's legacy will live on in name!
